  "texts": [
    "The impact of the regularization strength γ on our judges is investigated in Figures 5 to 7.",
    "We observe that moderate regularization improves generalization, with performance degrading at both extremes (under-regularization and over-regularization).",
    "This points to the importance of tuning γ.",
    "To avoid putting this burden on a human, we suggest setting the regularization strength γ automatically based on k-fold cross-validation.",
    "We use k = 5 in our experiments."
  ],
